1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 14=

21
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:26,330
Rou.

22
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,590
Dance one more piece for me.

23
00:01:28,350 --> 00:01:29,280
Your Majesty,

24
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,680
you've already seen

25
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,560
all the dances I've performed.

26
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,710
If I keep dancing the same ones,

27
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,710
they'll lose their charm.

28
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:40,910
But,

29
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:44,070
I've created a new dance recently.

30
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:46,350
It's called the Flower Picking Dance.

31
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,150
It's made

32
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,680
especially for you.

33
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:50,880
What are you waiting for?

34
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:52,590
Perform it for me to see.

35
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,120
But this dance

36
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,760
is missing one prop.

37
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,150
I can't perform it.

38
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,320
What's missing?

39
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,600
A single flower.

40
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,280
The flowers you gave me

41
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,590
are excellent,

42
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:10,520
but they come in pots and clusters.

43
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:13,360
If I pick just one,

44
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,520
it will lose its grandeur.

45
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,710
You want something grand

46
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:19,800
and bright colored.

47
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,560
I remember

48
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:24,470
there are peonies
in the Imperial Garden.

49
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,240
They're excellent.

50
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:27,960
Sixi.

51
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,910
I'm here.

52
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,960
Pass down my order.

53
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,560
Go to the Imperial Garden,

54
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,360
cut a beautiful peony,

55
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,910
and give it to the Noble Lady

56
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,630
as a dance prop.

57
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:38,990
Your Majesty,

58
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:41,080
but the peonies in the Imperial Garden

59
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:43,280
are always for Noble Consort.

60
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:44,800
No one else

61
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:46,910
is allowed to take them.

62
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,630
It's just a flower.

63
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,400
I can grant it to whomever I wish.

64
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:52,360
Others have no say in it.

65
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,750
Yes, Your Majesty.

66
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,520
Your Majesty,

67
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:29,710
this red hydrangea bloomed beautifully.

68
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:34,030
This Erqiao peony is bright enough.

69
00:03:37,910 --> 00:03:39,080
I remember

70
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:42,430
there were three Yao Huang peonies
this year.

71
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:45,000
Why is not one here today?

72
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,910
Your Ladyship,

73
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,080
the Yaohuang Peony is the most delicate.

74
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:50,080
The temperature dropped sharply
the other day.

75
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,030
And two pots withered.

76
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,590
Where is the third one?

77
00:03:53,330 --> 00:03:54,520
To answer you, Your Ladyship,

78
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,080
the last pot...

79
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,240
This morning,

80
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,840
Eunuch Sixi took it away.

81
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,590
He said His Majesty

82
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,510
bestowed it on Lady Xiao.

83
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,630
All of you leave!

84
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:11,560
Smash

85
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,120
all these flowers!

86
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,000
Your Ladyship, calm down.

87
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,510
Maybe Eunuch Sixi acted on his own.

88
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,870
His Majesty may not know.

89
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,870
May not know?

90
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,310
In this palace, other than His Majesty,

91
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,950
who would dare touch my peonies?

92
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,600
Lady Xiao.

93
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,360
That shameless maid!

94
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,920
Lady Xiao, look over there.

95
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,430
The lotuses are blooming beautifully.

96
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,310
Lotuses are lovely,

97
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:47,920
but not as beautiful as
the Imperial Garden peonies.

98
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:50,830
My favorite Yao Huang peony.

99
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,390
Seeing it every day

100
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:53,600
makes me feel refreshed.

101
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,160
But it's too delicate to care for.

102
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,190
Rest easy, Your Ladyship.

103
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:01,560
I have someone to tend it
with lukewarm water daily.

104
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,560
I don't slack off even at midnight.

105
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,790
What's wrong?

106
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:14,480
Something's up in the confinement room.

107
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:17,120
The head maid wants me to go there.

108
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:20,270
But you cannot be
left unattended either.

109
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,560
Go on.

110
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:24,360
I was just thinking of
taking a walk myself.

111
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,560
Lotus seeds are perfect this season.

112
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,630
Steaming them makes nourishing soup.

113
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,840
What was that sound?

114
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,240
Lady Xiao.

115
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,640
Lady Xiao.

116
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,800
Lady Xiao!

117
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,070
Help! Someone help!

118
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,230
Lady Xiao.

119
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,200
Hurry.

120
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,510
Help her back to her chamber.

121
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,190
Summon the Imperial Physician.

122
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,830
Lady Xiao fell.

123
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:34,120
This is happening far too early
in the story.

124
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:38,600
It's all my fault. I rushed to save her

125
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,680
and changed her fate.

126
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,070
This butterfly effect.

127
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,680
What else will it cause?

128
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,190
Your Majesty,

129
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:04,190
Lady Xiao nearly fell off the bridge
last night.

130
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:06,830
Then Lady Xiao, she...

131
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,310
Lady Xiao

132
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,920
was in low spirits last night.

133
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,560
So she went to
the Imperial Garden to relax,

134
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,830
but accidentally fell.

135
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,750
Her face is ruined.

136
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,800
Accidental fall?

137
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,510
Has the cause been found?

138
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,800
Noble Consort

139
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,800
sent the Punishment Office
to investigate.

140
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,430
Give her medicine and silver.

141
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,590
And take good care of her.

142
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:32,590
Yes.

143
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,400
Your Majesty!

144
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,170
Your Majesty!

145
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,310
It's me.

146
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,920
I'm Lady Xiao.

147
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,150
Your Majesty.

148
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,600
You must uphold justice for me.

149
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,630
My injury was no accident.

150
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:01,000
Someone meant to harm me.

151
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,640
This matter has been

152
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,630
investigated by Punishment Office
on Consort Lan's orders.

153
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,360
The conclusion was reached long ago.

154
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:08,040
You say someone tried to harm you.

155
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,270
Do you have proof?

156
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,270
I have no proof.

157
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,830
But all these incidents

158
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:16,870
are suspicious.

159
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,600
Consort Lan called it an accident

160
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,750
and closed my case.

161
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,920
I refuse to accept it!

162
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:23,040
I only beg you

163
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,830
to investigate fully.

164
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,040
And get me justice.

165
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,680
Harem affairs

166
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,270
have always been handled by Consort Lan

167
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,800
I'm busy with state affairs.

168
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,630
I can't interfere in everything.

169
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,110
Your Majesty,

170
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,840
I will die.

171
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,080
Your Majesty,

172
00:08:40,090 --> 00:08:41,840
my whole life is already ruined.

173
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,600
All I ask now is justice.

174
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,600
Your Majesty, can't you fulfill

175
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,360
this one wish?

176
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,510
The harem has its rules.

177
00:08:58,270 --> 00:08:59,320
How can I break the rules

178
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:00,870
for you alone?

179
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:03,120
One day of marriage
is a hundred days of kindness.

180
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,960
Can't you fulfill

181
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,750
this small wish?

182
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,040
How dare you!

183
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,670
You're just a Noble Lady.

184
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,630
How dare you call yourself his wife?

185
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:13,000
Have you lost your mind?

186
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,440
Your Majesty!

187
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,280
Stop her!

188
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,720
Let me go!

189
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,610
Your Majesty!

190
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:19,750
I beg you.

191
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,150
Your Majesty, Your Majesty!

192
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:23,790
Lady Xiao disgraced herself
before the throne.

193
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:24,750
One month confined.

194
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,360
Have the Physician attend her daily.

195
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,000
Don't bother me

196
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,510
with any petty matters.

197
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:31,710
Yes.

198
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,720
Your Majesty!

199
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:34,470
Take her away!

200
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:35,990
Your Majesty.

201
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,030
Your Majesty!

202
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,910
Your Majesty!

203
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,750
Make way for His Majesty.

204
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,600
His Majesty is

205
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,320
truly heartless.

206
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:48,030
She was once favored by him, after all.

207
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:51,840
Lady Xiao won his favor with her beauty,

208
00:09:52,100 --> 00:09:53,120
yet she never understood

209
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,120
that when beauty fades, so does love.

210
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,750
She shouldn't have come here today,

211
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:00,480
and certainly not let His Majesty
see her disfigured face.

212
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,030
His Majesty
might have cared for her before.

213
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:05,790
But after today,

214
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,320
that care

215
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:10,870
is probably gone.

216
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:14,550
(As expected of the harem champion
in the novel.)

217
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:18,480
You really know His Majesty well.

218
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:25,000
When I was thirteen,

219
00:10:25,220 --> 00:10:26,510
I resolved to enter the Palace.

220
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,270
Since then,

221
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:29,510
I've secretly

222
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:31,390
collected everything about His Majesty.

223
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:32,750
His

224
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:34,000
essays,

225
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,840
memorials,

226
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:35,700
and poems.

227
00:10:35,710 --> 00:10:37,270
I've read and memorized them all.

228
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,840
What kind of person is he?

229
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,870
In the entire harem,

230
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,670
no one knows better than I do.

231
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,630
The harem to him

232
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,150
is just a break from court

233
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:50,030
or a place
to carry on the imperial heirs.

234
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,910
No one can touch his heart.

235
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,960
Not even

236
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:58,840
me.

237
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,790
If you can think that way,

238
00:11:03,790 --> 00:11:06,480
you're better than most women here.

239
00:11:11,870 --> 00:11:12,910
Though His Majesty ordered

240
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,670
the Imperial Physician
to treat her daily.

241
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:17,360
But the Imperial Physician
sent by Consort Lan is perfunctory.

242
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,870
The medicine is useless.

243
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,320
Lady Xiao
has been vomiting blood for days.

244
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:22,440
She's not getting better.

245
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:24,870
I'm afraid she won't make it.

246
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,960
Lady Xiao,

247
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,960
this is Physician Ye Jin

248
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,960
sent from Cining Palace.

249
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,480
Hearing you're gravely ill,

250
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,390
so she's here to treat you.

251
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:34,800
No need.

252
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,150
Why save me?

253
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,790
I'd rather die.

254
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,240
If you die,

255
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,510
then the one who harmed you

256
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:44,320
will sleep well tonight.

257
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,270
Your illness

258
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,360
is not a fever.

259
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,480
Nor poison.

260
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,840
It's caused by melancholy.

261
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,080
If you stay calm and happy,

262
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,600
a few herbs will cure you.

263
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,870
But if you're sad every day,

264
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,480
melancholy builds up,

265
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,480
and even a divine physician
can't cure you.

266
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,630
My face has been disfigured.

267
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,000
I don't even know who harmed me.

268
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,360
Even His Majesty hates me now.

269
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,360
How can I stay calm?

270
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,270
Even just to find the truth

271
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,480
and seek justice,

272
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,150
you must live.

273
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:51,710
Biqing.

274
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,240
Miss Ye Jin,

275
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:54,840
Consort Lan requests your presence.

276
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,800
Alright.

277
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,600
These golden hair ornaments

278
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,390
were bestowed on you by Consort Lan.

279
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:12,600
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Ladyship.

280
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,840
Only...

281
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,240
I'm afraid

282
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,440
I can't accept this without merit.

283
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,390
If you think you have no merit,

284
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,790
then for now,

285
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:23,840
I'll give you a chance to earn merit.

286
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,670
What does Your Ladyship

287
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,320
wish me to do?

288
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:34,240
The Empress Dowager's birthday
is coming.

289
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:37,150
All concubines will attend the feast.

290
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,550
You run the Cining Palace kitchen,

291
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:41,120
so you can easily get to the food.

292
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,200
Then

293
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,630
put this packet of medicine

294
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:46,030
into Consort Duan's food.

295
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,600
I dare not.

296
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,000
Spare me, Your Ladyship.

297
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:50,910
What are you afraid of?

298
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,150
This is called Qingteng Herb.

299
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,390
It's just a purgative.

300
00:13:54,790 --> 00:13:56,630
It was due to
her misbehaving while pregnant

301
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,030
and defying Consort Lan.

302
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,870
Consort Lan just wants to give her

303
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:00,960
a small warning.

304
00:14:01,390 --> 00:14:02,670
If you do this well,

305
00:14:02,770 --> 00:14:03,750
no one will dare to question

306
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,630
the food
from the Empress Dowager's palace.

307
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,270
And no one will suspect you.

308
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,990
I... but...

309
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:10,710
Your Ladyship, I...

310
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,000
You won't do this small favor?

311
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:14,790
Was your loyalty to Consort Lan

312
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:16,000
all a lie?

313
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,840
No.

314
00:14:16,850 --> 00:14:19,550
I always reward and punish fairly.

315
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,480
If this matter is done well,

316
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:24,200
I'll reward you greatly.

317
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,360
But if you fail,

318
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:28,510
I have plenty of ways

319
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:32,510
to make you vanish from the harem.

320
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:41,400
♪I am but an outsider♪

321
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,600
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

322
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:47,880
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

323
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:52,120
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

324
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,640
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

325
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:03,200
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

326
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,720
♪I know how this story ends♪

327
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:10,280
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

328
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:14,720
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

329
00:15:19,680 --> 00:15:23,000
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

330
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:26,280
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

331
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:29,560
♪A history that no one can search♪

332
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:33,080
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

333
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,880
♪I am but an outsider♪

334
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:37,120
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

335
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:41,160
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

336
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:45,840
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

337
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:53,160
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

338
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:56,520
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

339
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:59,000
♪I know how this story ends♪

340
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:03,160
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

341
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:06,440
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

342
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:10,240
♪Please forget me and move on♪

343
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:16,480
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

344
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:28,000
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

345
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:41,280
♪When do I finally wake♪
